Pupunta ako para sayo.

24
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:43,460
Kailangan bang maging malupit?

25
00:02:43,830 --> 00:02:45,390
Fine, hindi na ako magtatanong. Masaya ngayon?

26
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:47,070
Araw-araw,

27
00:02:47,070 --> 00:02:47,950
