121
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:32,180
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

122
00:07:34,710 --> 00:07:35,550
Chen Hui,

123
00:07:36,620 --> 00:07:39,030
ngayon ang pinaka masayang araw
Matagal ko na.

124
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:40,630
Songge,

125
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:43,300
