183
00:10:11,540 --> 00:10:13,660
Tungkol sa kaso
pinangangasiwaan ng aming istasyon at ng Kriminal

184
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:14,990
Brigada ng Pagsisiyasat
ng municipal PSB,

185
00:10:14,990 --> 00:10:16,950
