Ipikit mo ang iyong mga mata.

749
00:30:50,870 --> 00:30:51,750
Okay.

750
00:30:51,760 --> 00:30:52,750
Maaari mong buksan ang mga ito ngayon.

751
00:30:55,020 --> 00:30:55,880
Paano?

752
00:30:55,900 --> 00:30:56,750
Mukhang maganda ba ito?

753
00:30:57,580 --> 00:30:58,420
Mukhang mahusay.

754
00:31:01,820 --> 00:31:02,660
salamat po.

755
00:31:03,630 --> 00:31:04,580
Ito ay wala.

756
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:07,540
Ito ang ating bagong simula.

757
00:31:07,540 --> 00:31:09,660
(Yingxiong)

758
00:31:13,190 --> 00:31:15,870
gagawin ko.

759
00:31:15,870 --> 00:31:17,230
Tatay,

760
00:31:17,230 --> 00:31:18,300
magpahinga ka na.

761
00:31:18,300 --> 00:31:19,670
Manood ka na lang mula rito.

762
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:20,920
Halika na.

763
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:22,210
Sige, dito na tayo.

764
00:31:23,300 --> 00:31:24,500
Ano ang lahat ng kaguluhan na ito ngayon?

765
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:26,150
Hayaan mo akong gawin ito.

766
00:31:26,150 --> 00:31:26,990
Dad, hayaan mo na ako.

767
00:31:26,990 --> 00:31:28,670
- Kaya ko.
- Umupo ka na lang. Umupo ka.

768
00:31:28,670 --> 00:31:29,740
Hindi ba ito ang gamit mula sa

769
00:31:29,740 --> 00:31:30,670
noong may sakit si Hui?

770
00:31:30,670 --> 00:31:33,060
Ito ay nakakasira sa paningin at tumatagal ng espasyo,
kaya inalis ko na lahat.

771
00:31:33,060 --> 00:31:34,230
Buti na lang inayos.

772
00:31:41,230 --> 00:31:42,080
Tang.

773
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:42,940
Direk Chen.

774
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:45,580
Nandito ako para i-update ka
sa kaso ni Gao Ying.

775
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:46,430
Dito.

776
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:48,740
Ang resulta ng autopsy ni Gao Ying
nasa labas, tama?

777
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:49,580
Oo.

778
00:31:49,580 --> 00:31:51,230
Bagama't ang bangkay ay inilibing nang napakatagal

779
00:31:51,230 --> 00:31:52,950
ang daming ebidensya
ay nawasak sa biyolohikal na paraan,

780
00:31:52,950 --> 00:31:54,230
may nakita kaming pulbos

781
00:31:54,230 --> 00:31:56,060
sa katawan,
at ito ay potassium manganate.

782
00:31:56,060 --> 00:31:57,540
Ito ang parehong substance na matatagpuan sa

783
00:31:57,540 --> 00:31:58,740
Yu Susu at katawan ni Lu Yuan.

784
00:31:59,230 --> 00:32:00,300
Napakagandang balita iyan.

785
00:32:01,500 --> 00:32:02,340
Tang,

786
00:32:02,710 --> 00:32:05,070
ano ang iniisip ng municipal PSB
tungkol sa pagsasama ng mga kaso?

787
00:32:05,190 --> 00:32:06,060
Sabi ng municipal PSB

788
00:32:06,060 --> 00:32:07,580
may direct na ngayon
pisikal na ebidensya na nag-uugnay

789
00:32:07,580 --> 00:32:08,910
Ang kaso ni Gao Ying sa kaso ni Huo Kaiming.

790
00:32:08,910 --> 00:32:10,740
Maaari nating simulan ang proseso
ng pagsasama-sama ng mga kaso.

791
00:32:11,230 --> 00:32:12,070
Tang,

792
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:13,340
salamat po.

793
00:32:13,340 --> 00:32:14,180
Sige.

794
00:32:17,950 --> 00:32:19,470
Pumunta at kunin ang nilagang karne ng tupa.

795
00:32:19,470 --> 00:32:20,310
May magandang balita ako.

796
00:32:20,500 --> 00:32:21,470
Anong magandang balita?

797
00:32:22,510 --> 00:32:24,780
Lumabas na ang resulta ng autopsy ni Gao Ying.

798
00:32:24,780 --> 00:32:26,300
Hindi ito kusang pagkasunog.

799
00:32:26,410 --> 00:32:27,670
Sa wakas nakahanap na kami ng ebidensya,

800
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:28,780
para mapagsama natin ang mga kaso.

801
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:29,990
Talagang magandang balita iyan.

802
00:32:29,990 --> 00:32:31,580
Sige. Magluluto ako ng karne ng tupa.

803
00:32:31,580 --> 00:32:32,420
Okay.

804
00:32:32,670 --> 00:32:33,540
Tatay,

805
00:32:33,540 --> 00:32:34,780
may mutton tayo ngayong gabi.

806
00:32:36,020 --> 00:32:36,990
Mabuti.

807
00:32:36,990 --> 00:32:37,830
Tatay,

808
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:39,030
pasok na tayo sa loob.

809
00:32:39,740 --> 00:32:40,580
Pumasok na tayo.

810
00:32:42,340 --> 00:32:44,630
Sabihin mo sa akin,
nahuli na ba ang kriminal na iyon?

811
00:32:44,790 --> 00:32:46,540
Kami pa rin

812
00:32:46,540 --> 00:32:47,430
pagkatapos ng kriminal.

813
00:32:48,560 --> 00:32:49,430
Nanghuhuli ng kriminal

814
00:32:49,430 --> 00:32:50,870
ay parang nagpapalipad ng saranggola.

815
00:32:50,870 --> 00:32:53,260
Mas malakas ang hangin,
mas kailangan mong ilabas ang linya.

816
00:32:53,260 --> 00:32:54,100
Yan ang tawag nila

817
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:55,510
"pagbalanse ng tensyon at pagpapahinga".

818
00:32:56,100 --> 00:32:58,710
Kung hindi, masisira ang string ng saranggola.

819
00:32:58,710 --> 00:32:59,630
Ang inilalarawan mo

820
00:32:59,630 --> 00:33:00,820
ay kung paano manghuli ng isda.

821
00:33:03,990 --> 00:33:04,990
sabi ko sayo

822
00:33:04,990 --> 00:33:06,150
Gusto ko talaga

823
00:33:06,330 --> 00:33:07,910
pumunta sa ilalim ng kasong ito.

824
00:33:07,910 --> 00:33:08,750
Kita mo?

825
00:33:09,630 --> 00:33:10,910
Sigurado yan.

826
00:33:10,910 --> 00:33:12,820
Pagdating sa mga kaso,
hindi ka kailanman nagkamali.

827
00:33:13,570 --> 00:33:14,740
Siguradong maganda ang mata mo.

828
00:33:15,390 --> 00:33:16,430
Sapat na.

829
00:33:16,430 --> 00:33:17,670
Ang anumang papuri ay magiging labis.

830
00:33:21,020 --> 00:33:22,100
Bakit pakiramdam ko ay

831
00:33:22,870 --> 00:33:24,300
tumaba ka ba lately?

832
00:33:25,470 --> 00:33:26,310
Imposible yun.

833
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:28,710
Hindi pa nalulutas ang kaso.

834
00:33:28,710 --> 00:33:29,910
Paano ako tataba?

835
00:33:33,230 --> 00:33:34,100
Naalala ko noon,

836
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:36,260
nung una kitang nakilala,

837
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:37,500
mukhang fit ka.

838
00:33:38,630 --> 00:33:39,980
Huwag isipin ang mga nakaraang kaluwalhatian.

839
00:33:42,230 --> 00:33:43,500
Noong mga araw na iyon,

840
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:45,300
sinuot mo ang iyong buhok sa dalawang maliliit na tirintas.

841
00:33:45,300 --> 00:33:46,470
Ito ay talagang medyo maganda.

842
00:33:47,150 --> 00:33:48,260
Naaalala mo pa ba ito?

843
00:33:48,260 --> 00:33:49,300
Paano ko makakalimutan?

844
00:33:51,100 --> 00:33:52,670
Parang

845
00:33:52,670 --> 00:33:54,710
mahigit 20 taon na ang nakalipas.

846
00:33:57,340 --> 00:33:58,180
Hoy babae.

847
00:33:58,870 --> 00:34:01,470
Tingnan ko
sa iyong Chairman Mao badge.

848
00:34:01,470 --> 00:34:02,330
Hiramin natin ito

849
00:34:02,330 --> 00:34:03,340
at makita ito.

850
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:04,740
anong ginagawa mo

851
00:34:04,740 --> 00:34:05,700
- Ano ang ginagawa natin?
- Ano ang ginagawa natin?

852
00:34:05,710 --> 00:34:07,020
Ibigay mo na lang dito!

853
00:34:07,470 --> 00:34:08,350
anong ginagawa mo

854
00:34:08,350 --> 00:34:09,540
Tumigil ka!

855
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:10,380
Tumigil ka.

856
00:34:12,180 --> 00:34:13,020
Ikaw ang humihingi nito!

857
00:34:16,350 --> 00:34:18,140
Ibalik mo yan! Ilipat!

858
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:18,990
Napakatapang mo.

859
00:34:18,990 --> 00:34:19,830
Ilipat ito!

860
00:34:21,540 --> 00:34:22,390
Magwala ka!

861
00:34:22,530 --> 00:34:23,510
Ano ba naman?

862
00:34:24,700 --> 00:34:25,540
okay ka lang ba?

863
00:34:25,950 --> 00:34:26,790
ayos lang ako.

864
00:34:27,350 --> 00:34:28,190
salamat po.

865
00:34:45,310 --> 00:34:46,170
Sandali lang.

866
00:34:46,180 --> 00:34:47,070
Naaalala mo pa ba?

867
00:34:47,990 --> 00:34:49,270
Noon, si Gao Ying

868
00:34:50,020 --> 00:34:51,660
laging may ganitong rainbow glow
sa kanyang ulo.

869
00:34:52,660 --> 00:34:53,790
Pagtama ng araw,

870
00:34:53,790 --> 00:34:54,700
naging makulay ang lahat.

871
00:34:54,700 --> 00:34:55,540
Medyo maganda ang hitsura nito.

872
00:34:56,830 --> 00:34:57,670
hindi ko maalala.

873
00:34:59,870 --> 00:35:00,710
galit ka ba

874
00:35:02,620 --> 00:35:03,700
nagtatanong lang naman ako.

875
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:04,540
anong mali?

876
00:35:05,970 --> 00:35:06,830
Oo.

877
00:35:06,830 --> 00:35:08,020
Noon, madalas siyang magkaroon ng

878
00:35:08,020 --> 00:35:09,100
isang glow o isang bagay

879
00:35:09,100 --> 00:35:11,100
sa kanyang buhok o sa kanyang katawan.

880
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:13,020
Tinanong ko siya tungkol dito minsan.

881
00:35:13,020 --> 00:35:14,040
Sabi niya

882
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:14,950
ito ay dahil sa kanyang ama

883
00:35:14,970 --> 00:35:16,990
nagtrabaho sa lumang coal washing plant.

884
00:35:16,990 --> 00:35:19,310
Madalas siyang pumunta doon
para dalhan siya ng pagkain.

885
00:35:19,310 --> 00:35:20,870
Sa tuwing babalik siya noon,

886
00:35:20,870 --> 00:35:22,060
sa kanyang katawan

887
00:35:22,060 --> 00:35:23,870
at sa kanyang buhok,
magkakaroon ng glow na iyon.

888
00:35:23,870 --> 00:35:25,580
Parang naging

889
00:35:25,580 --> 00:35:27,470
mula sa tubig sa coal washing pool.

890
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:31,580
Ang lumang coal washing plant.

891
00:35:45,740 --> 00:35:55,540
(Heyi Coal Washing Plant, Fengyang Town)

892
00:36:16,750 --> 00:36:17,590
ano ito?

893
00:36:23,470 --> 00:36:24,310
Isang motorsiklo.

894
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:30,180
Napakaraming kamukha nito

895
00:36:30,180 --> 00:36:31,350
ang inilarawan ni Ma Heping.

896
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:34,430
Sa babaeng may peklat?

897
00:36:34,430 --> 00:36:35,620
Malamang.

898
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:36,500
Pumunta ka.

899
00:36:36,500 --> 00:36:37,340
Tumingin tingin sa paligid.

900
00:37:07,910 --> 00:37:08,750
Mabilis.

901
00:37:09,470 --> 00:37:10,310
Humanap ka ng poste.

902
00:37:10,870 --> 00:37:11,710
Okay.

903
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,700
Direk Chen.

904
00:37:34,180 --> 00:37:35,310
May kung ano sa ilalim.

905
00:37:37,220 --> 00:37:38,540
Medyo mabigat.

906
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:39,380
Bigyan mo ako ng kamay.

907
00:37:44,390 --> 00:37:45,230
Buksan ito at tingnan.

908
00:37:53,350 --> 00:37:54,310
May isa pang layer.

909
00:38:03,430 --> 00:38:04,270
Ito ay cough syrup.

910
00:38:04,860 --> 00:38:07,700
(Peidun Cough Syrup)

911
00:38:07,700 --> 00:38:08,830
Puno na sila.

